          <unittitle>Series 4: Southern Christian Leadership Conference (SCLC), 1969-1988</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent id="aspace_8d2e3a6a2d607dfbd7bcbdf44eb92208">
          <head>Scope and Contents</head>
          <p>This series contains meeting minutes, conference packets, brochures, newsletters, and reports of the SCLC which was closely involved with efforts to establish a King Holiday.  The materials are primarily from the 1980s but also include a few historical documents from SCLC, which Dr. King established in the early 1960s.  The series also contains the SCLC magazine, SCLC, from 1986-1990.</p>
